trans-unit.source: Specifies where an offset is applied to a window element.
trans-unit.target: 指定其中一个偏移量应用于窗口元素。

trans-unit.source: The OffsetType values represent the return values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetEnumValue%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method when it is called with an argument value of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.EnumProperty?displayProperty=fullName>.
